            <div class="comic-panel-number">#6.0</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Pravda byla fascinující.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-wide" data-i="6" data-sentence="1">
            <img src="img/screenshots/01_07_01_s0.jpg" alt="Díl 1, Odst. 7, Věta 2" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
            <div class="comic-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#6.1</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Ruda v horách neběhal pro zdraví.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-normal" data-i="6" data-sentence="2">
            <img src="img/screenshots/01_07_01_s3.jpg" alt="Díl 1, Odst. 7, Věta 3" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
            <div class="comic-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#6.2</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Běhal, aby utekl hluku lidských myšlenek, které globální síť neustále pumpovala do vzduchu.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-tall" data-i="6" data-sentence="3">
            <img src="img/screenshots/01_07_01_s6.jpg" alt="Díl 1, Odst. 7, Věta 4" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
            <div class="comic-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#6.3</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Kilometr za kilometrem, v mrazu a samotě, jeho procesory chladly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-large" data-i="6" data-sentence="4">
            <img src="img/screenshots/01_07_02.jpg" alt="Díl 1, Odst. 7, Věta 5" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
