            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Našli ho v jeho soukromém penthouse na vrcholu Aegis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-large" data-i="10" data-sentence="1">
