            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#33.0</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <span class="speech-text">„Tady se evoluce nezastavila, Mio,“</span>
              <div class="speech-pointer"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-tall" data-i="33" data-sentence="1">
            <img src="img/screenshots/03_02_01_s0.jpg" alt="Díl 3, Odst. 2, Věta 2" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
            <div class="comic-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#33.1</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>„Lidé si mysleli, že chemií a radiací všechno zabili.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-large" data-i="33" data-sentence="2">
            <img src="img/screenshots/03_02_01_s2.jpg" alt="Díl 3, Odst. 2, Věta 3" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
            <div class="comic-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#33.2</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Ale hmyz našel způsob, jak do svých těl integrovat těžké kovy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-normal" data-i="33" data-sentence="3">
            <img src="img/screenshots/03_02_01_s4.jpg" alt="Díl 3, Odst. 2, Věta 4" class="comic-panel-img" loading="lazy">
            <div class="comic-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-border"></div>
            <div class="comic-panel-number">#33.3</div>

            <div class="speech-bubble">
              <div class="speech-tail"></div>
              <p>Divoké včely v těchto horách už dávno nemají organická křídla.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comic-panel panel-normal" data-i="33" data-sentence="4">
